			  	first of all, in regards to off center fleets, if i recall correctly, they are there after the original capital fleet is killed in a battle, another one just takes its place. In regards to your problem, try not scrolling down on the screen until the screen is fully loaded, that is usually why the fleets will jump ahead. Hope that helps			   <P align=right></P>
