			    <HR color=#000000 SIZE=-1>
			  	stalin:<br />
<br />
For IE, you have to wait until the page is fully loaded before trying to place fleets. Once the screen is fully loaded DO NOT SCROLL, rather just click on the fleets you want, move them to their formation spot, right click to give them commands etc and it will work perfectly (I use the classic java for fleet formation in IE)<br />
<br />
For Mozilla, I find only the new fleet formation java works for me. Again, wait for it to load and place fleets, set orders and then accept the formation. <br />
<br />
You can't scroll your screen at all when doing any fleet formation work, and you cannot start trying to place them before you have let the page load completely.<br />
<br />
Houston			   <P align=right></P>
